<h2> To preserve a text with the original format we use "pre"</h2>
  <pre>
  My Bonnie lies over the ocean.

  My Bonnie lies over the sea.

  My Bonnie lies over the ocean.

  Oh, bring back my Bonnie to me.
  </pre>

<h2> To set the color of the paragraph to "blue", and HTML attribute, we use style </h2>
<p style="color:blue;">This is a paragraph.</p>
